{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Sol Cesto, your goal is to explore a random dungeon in search of the lost sun. Each screen has 4 rooms you can enter with a click. You choose the room, but not the outcome: an enemy, a chest, or a secret could be waiting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, you'll need to weigh the risks of each room. Your character will grow stronger, and with the help of items and skills, you can manipulate chance to tilt the odds in your favor. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>25 floors</strong> to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2 playable characters</strong> (the Knight and the Warrior), each with unique stats, items, and powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>9 monsters</strong>, including <strong>3 with special abilities</strong>: the Magician, the Musician, and the Demon Rabbit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6 locations</strong> to upgrade your character: Demon Statues, the Merchant, the Blacksmith, the Fountain, and the Well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>10 items</strong> available from the Merchant to improve your chances of survival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6 fountain items</strong> to bless your run and make it easier.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nearly <strong>20 cursed teeth</strong> to collect, altering the game\u2019s rules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About <strong>10 permanent upgrades</strong> to help with future runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733439454","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733439454","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876270/capsu